Redis is used because it is extremely fast, scalable, and reliable for real-time systems (Banking, Trading, Microservices).

Here are the key reasons 👇

⚡ 1. In-Memory Speed (Super Fast)

Redis stores data in RAM, not disk.

Response time: 1–5 ms

Much faster than DB (20–200 ms)

Used for:

