12️⃣ Common Interview Questions
Q1: @Cacheable vs @CachePut vs @CacheEvict?
Annotation	Purpose
Cacheable	Read from cache / store result
CachePut	Update cache
CacheEvict	Remove cache
Q2: What is Cache Stampede?

Many requests hit DB when cache expires simultaneously.

Solution

Use TTL + random delay

Use distributed lock

Use refresh ahead

Q3: When NOT to cache?

Highly dynamic data (like live balance)

Huge datasets

Sensitive data (password)

Q4: Redis vs In-Memory Cache?
Redis	In-Memory
Distributed	Single instance
Persistent	Not
Production ready	Dev only
